data.title: LOST.TV - 2010 K5 KLASSIC HIGHLIGHTS
data.description:
LOST.TV - Chucky called this contests, "Like the US Open but at D-Street". Not sure if it was as big but it was definately just as fun. Check out the highlights of Aaron "Gorkin" Cormican, Cory Lopez, Teddy Navarro, Killian Garland (he won the contest) and D-Street local Darrel Goodrum surfing in this year's K5 Klassic in Encinitas, California.

Music by The Scrid Hunters

data.title: ...LOST SURF SKATE CONTEST IN PORTA ALEGRE, BRAZIL
data.description: There's no better way to introduce the new surf inspired collection of ...LOST surf skates then to take it to the one of the longest snake runs in the world and put on a contest of surf-skate slashes! Porto Alegre, Brazil home of The Marinha, Skate Park with a snake run that's over 500ft long. and over 30 years old.

data.title: LOST.TV - NOAH ALANI GOLF CLUB CAM DOWNHILL SKATEBOARD RUN
data.description: Professional fun guy and videographer Noah Alani (he's Kolohe's guy) and ...Lost SurfSkate rider Juan-Pablo go on a downhill skate run in San Clemente with Noah's GoPro camera strapped to the end of a golf club. We're not sure what Noah is riding but Juan-Pablo is on his ...Lost SurfSkate pro model - the "Blacksheep Bomber". Juan-Pablo was also testing out his new leather suit that he is borrowing from his friend so it's not really his but he's going to use it in his race next weekend. Check the video below.
